snippet.title: PARANORMAL RECORDS | GAMEPLAY TEASER (UNREAL ENGINE 5)
snippet.description:
Paranormal Records is a next-generation horror game made on Unreal Engine 5. A unique narrative experience from the perspective of a video camera. The protagonist, the host of a TV show about the paranormal, is filming a report about a missing patient, in an abandoned hospital.

Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2404960/Paranormal_Records/?beta=0

Contact us - info@bbgame.ru
